Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:09.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,平凡的三年级小学生\N\N高町奈叶与命运意外邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:15.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,坚信旭日的勇气　紧握魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:22.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,我能够理解　钢铁般的意志\N\N是难以动摇　也难以舍弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:27.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是最初亦是最后的全力一战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,我将以自己全部的魔法来回应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,我愿以千百次的呼唤　换得你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔法少女奈叶　要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,母亲总是那样地慈祥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,总是亲切的呼唤我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎么样　很漂亮吧？　艾丽茜娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾丽茜娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,不对啊　妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是菲特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,来　过来吧　艾丽茜娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　真可爱　艾丽茜娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,算了　没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,我深爱着慈祥母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:46.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,第十一话\N\N「时光彼岸的追忆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,战斗开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,不过　难以置信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺君居然批准这种赌斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　奈叶能赢当然最好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,但战斗结果其实无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,利用奈叶为我们争取到的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.61,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们做好追踪菲特的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,成败就全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,可别让她逃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:41.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,但不将普蕾茜亚{\fnsimhei}·{\r}泰斯特罗莎\N\N的家庭与事故详情转告奈叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,我还是希望奈叶能取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以现在不要给她增添迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.99,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Photon Lancer{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光子灵枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.79,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,300)\t(0,1000,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Divine Shooter{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天神灵弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.94,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Scythe Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光镰形态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.87,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)d\t(0,1500,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Round Shield{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔力环盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.23,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Flash Move{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}瞬速移动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.04,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Scythe Slash{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光镰裂斩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.84,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}Fire{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:07.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,起初她只是个魔力高强的外行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,但现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,出招既快又狠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,稍有迟疑　输的人便是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.89,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H800BBBB&)}Phalanx Shift{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}狂雷军威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H800BBBB&)}雷光枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,不好　菲特是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶　我这就援助你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾尔芙和尤诺君都不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是一对一的全力决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,是属于我与菲特的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是　菲特的这一招真的很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,阿尔卡斯　克洛塔斯　艾吉亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,疾风的天神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,遵从召唤奔腾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,巴勒基尔　扎鲁哥尔　布洛泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H800BBBB&)}光子灵枪{\fnSimHei}·{\fnYouYuan}狂雷军威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,驰骋吧！　发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:50.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,攻击结束后　枷锁也就解开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.88,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\t(0,700,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Divine──{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天神──
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,轮到我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.51,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H8000BB&}Buster{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}──烈破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,直击！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,必须坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,不能输给她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,尝尝我这招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,天神烈破的发展形态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.53,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\t(0,1500,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Starlight Breaker{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}星光聚裂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,枷锁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,这便是我的全力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:59.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\t(1200,2400,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}星光聚裂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.98,Default1,,0,0,0,,好…　好强的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,哇…　菲特还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,对不起　你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,可以算我赢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,看来是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.76,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Put out{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}释放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:31.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,还能飞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,好　奈叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,先回收圣石之种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,然后带她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:43.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,等等…　来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:44.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:02.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:04.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,物质传送会轻易暴露自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,锁定坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,已经锁定　设定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.81,Default1,,0,0,0,,武装局员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.35,Default1,,0,0,0,,由传送门出动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,立刻逮捕普蕾茜亚{\fnSimHei}·{\r}泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的身体已承受不住次元魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,刚才的传送已将位置暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,她还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,是该启程的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,第二小队　传送成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,第一小队　开始侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,另外…　菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,不能让她目睹母亲被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶　带她去别的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊…　是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,不如到我的房间去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,全员　侵入中央殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,普蕾茜亚{\fnSimHei}·{\r}泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:57.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,因违反时空管理法\N\N并攻击管理局舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,你被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,解除武装　到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,守住那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,这里有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,这…　这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,不要靠近我的艾丽茜娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,危险！　快防御！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,不好　快送局员们返航！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,明…　明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾丽…　茜娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,坐标锁定　0120503
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,锁定　传送准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,已经不行了　我们没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:52.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,仅靠9颗太古遗产\N\N不知能否到达「阿尔哈扎德」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,但已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,不必再忍受失去女儿悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:09.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,也不必再把人偶当作女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,我说的就是你　菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,我把艾丽茜娅的记忆给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,但你却只有外表像她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:27.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,根本就是个毫无用处的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,在最初的事故中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:36.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,普蕾茜亚失去了亲生女儿\N\N艾丽茜娅{\fnsimhei}·{\r}泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,她最后进行的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,是不同于使役魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,而又超越使役魔的人工生命技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,以及使死者复苏的秘术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:55.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,「F.A.T.E」是她当时的\N\N研究的开发代号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,你调查的真详细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,是啊　你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是　不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,研究一点也不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,人工生命终归是人工产物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,无法替代逝去的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾丽茜娅的笑容要更加灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:26.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾丽茜娅尽管有时任性\N\N却很是乖巧而听话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,别说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,与艾丽茜娅的每时每刻都充满温馨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,你终究不过是艾丽茜娅的仿制品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:46.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,枉费我给了你艾丽茜娅的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,别说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,别再说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:57.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,你只是艾丽茜娅复活前\N\N我用于安抚自己的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以我不再需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,快从我的眼前消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,求求你　不要再说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,告诉你一件事吧　菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,自从造出你以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,我一直都非常非常厌恶你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:45.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:46.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,已成功回收了局员们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,不…　不好了不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,快看这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,建筑物内出现众多魔力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:57.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,庭院内出现魔力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,个个都是A级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,总数60…　80…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:35.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,还在继续增加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,普蕾茜亚{\fnSimHei}·{\r}泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,你到底打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:04.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,我不希望我们的旅程遭人打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们就要启程了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,去寻匿那遗失的圣都\N\N──「阿尔哈扎德」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,难道你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们要凭借这力量启程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,去找回…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,失去的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,是次元震！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:42.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,超过中级规模
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,采取抗震防御
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,展开异相屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,9颗圣石之种发动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,次元震的等级正在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,保持传送可能的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,向影响较弱的空域移动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,明…　明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,乱次系数扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,这样下去将引发次元断层
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,阿尔…　哈扎德…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,我去阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:09.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,打开传送门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,遗失的圣都　阿尔哈扎德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,失落的禁断秘术所沉睡的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:22.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,你打算去那里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,你以为能找回流逝的过去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:38.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,无论使用怎样的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:42.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,都不可能重新找回过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:14.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,我与艾丽茜娅将在阿尔哈扎德\N\N挽回过去的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:14.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,被引发的次元震
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.82,0:25:18.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,为了阻止普蕾茜亚　我们闯入时光庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:21.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶的世界　我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.83,0:25:23.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,为了不使众多世界因此灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.71,0:25:26.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,这时　菲特又会怎样抉择？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:31.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,下集　魔法少女奈叶　第十二话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:33.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,宿命终结的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.63,0:25:37.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,莉莉卡露玛吉卡露　我会坚持到最后
